long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension occasionally injects NYTimes articles into Foxnews.

When a person visits foxnews.com, it will sometimes change one of the top three articles with a nytimes article. There is a 1 in 5 chance an article will be changed. If they are clicked, the article is displayed.

This is intended as a parody app and should not be taken seriously.
